	"system": {
		"description": {
			"value": "<p><strong>Materials:</strong> You require a sprinkle of holy water and diamonds worth at least 25,000 gold. This spell consumes this material.</p><p><strong>Healing</strong></p><ul><li><p>You restore life to a creature that has been dead for no longer than 200 years, provided it did not die of old age. The creature’s soul must be free and willing to return.</p></li><li><p>The creature is restored with all its hit points.</p></li><li><p>All wounds are closed, poisons are neutralized, diseases cured, and curses lifted.</p></li><li><p>Damaged or missing organs and limbs are replaced.</p></li><li><p>If the creature was &amp;reference[undead], it is restored to its original living form.</p></li><li><p>If no body exists, you may speak the creature’s name. A new body is created, and the creature appears in an unoccupied space within 10 ft. of you.</p></li></ul>",
